---
title: Buffalo-Style Chicken Breasts Flatbreads with Ranch-Dressed Slaw
description: This is a meal for those who are always torn between classic pub fare and pizza; tonight, you don't have to decide! Spicy, tangy DIY buffalo sauce is smothered on soft flatbreads, topped with roasted chicken thighs and mozzarella, then drizzled with a healthy helping of creamy ranch. It's a win-win!
